%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
\begin{frame}
\hilite<1> \frametitle{课题研究内容}
\pause
我们考虑如下的分数阶次扩散方程：
\begin{align}
&_0^CD_t^{\alpha}u(x,t)\!+\!\frac{{{{\partial}^2}}}{{{\partial}{x^2}}}\!\Big({\omega}(x)\frac{{{{\partial}^2}u(x,t)}}{{{\partial}{x^2}}}\Big)\!+\!{\kappa}u(x,t)\!=\!f(x,t), 0\!<\!x\!<\! L,0\!<\!t\!\le\! T,\label{eq:1}\\
& u(x,0)=\varphi (x),~~0 < x < L, \label{eq:2}
\end{align}
其中 ${\kappa}$ 是一个非负常数, $\omega(x), \varphi (x)$ 以及 $f(x,t)$ 都是给定的足够光滑的函数,${\kappa}u(x,t)$代表阻尼项, $f(x,t)$代表外力。假设存在两个常量 $c _ 1 $ 和 $c _ 2 $ 满足 $0 < { c _ 1} \leq \omega(x) \leq c _ 2 $对 $0 \leq x \leq L $成立。$0<\alpha<1$,$~_0^CD_t^{\alpha}u(x,t)$ 表示Caputo分数阶导数,其定义为：
\begin{align*}
~_0^CD_t^{\alpha}u(x,t)=\frac{1}{{\Gamma (1-{\alpha})}}\int_0^t {\frac{\partial u(x,s)}{\partial s}\frac{{1}}{{{{(t-s )}^{\alpha}}}}ds}.
\end{align*}
\end{frame}




%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
\begin{frame}
\hilite<1> \frametitle{课题研究内容}
\pause
我们拟在$\mathcal{L}2\!-\!{1_{\sigma}}$公式的基础上建立关于四阶空间变系数次扩散方程的高阶快速差分格式，并且考虑第二Dirichlet边界条件\eqref{eq:3}-\eqref{eq:4} 和第一Dirichlet边界条件\eqref{eq:5}-\eqref{eq:6}。此外,为了提高计算效率,降低计算复杂度, 我们打算运用$\mathcal{FL}2\!-\!1_{\sigma}$公式[14]构造一个快速差分格式。
\begin{align}
& u(0,t)={{\alpha}_1}(t),~u(L,t)={{\alpha}_2}(t),~~0 \le t \le T,\label{eq:3}\\
& \frac{{{{\partial}^2}u(0,t)}}{{{\partial}{x^2}}}={{\beta}_1}(t),~\frac{{{{\partial}^2}u(L,t)}}{{{\partial}{x^2}}}={{\beta}_2}(t),~~0 \le t \le T.\label{eq:4}
\end{align}

\begin{align}
& u(0,t)={{\alpha}_3}(t),~u(L,t)={{\alpha}_4}(t),~~0 \le t \le T,\label{eq:5}\\
& \frac{{{{\partial}}u(0,t)}}{{{\partial}{x}}}={{\beta}_3}(t),~\frac{{{{\partial}}u(L,t)}}{{{\partial}{x}}}={{\beta}_4}(t),~~0 \le t \le T,\label{eq:6}
\end{align}
\end{frame}

